@endpoint GET /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Sql/managedInstances/{managedInstanceName}/operations
@desc Gets a list of operations performed on the managed instance.
@required {resourceGroupName: any # The name of the resource group that contains the resource. You can obtain this value from the Azure Resource Manager API or the portal., managedInstanceName: any # The name of the managed instance., subscriptionId: any # The subscription ID that identifies an Azure subscription., api-version: any # The API version to use for the request.}
@returns(200) The request for getting managed instance operations has been executed successfully.

@endpoint GET /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Sql/managedInstances/{managedInstanceName}/operations/{operationId}
@desc Gets a management operation on a managed instance.
@required {resourceGroupName: any # The name of the resource group that contains the resource. You can obtain this value from the Azure Resource Manager API or the portal., managedInstanceName: any # The name of the managed instance., operationId: any, subscriptionId: any # The subscription ID that identifies an Azure subscription., api-version: any # The API version to use for the request.}
@returns(200) Successfully retrieved the specified managed instance operation.

